---
// Sticky impossible-to-miss banner for parody guides. Mounted at the very
// top of <ParodyLayout> so a screenshot of any parody content also captures
// the "this is satire" notice.
---

<div class="not-prose sticky top-0 z-30 border-b-2 border-amber-500 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/60 text-amber-950 dark:text-amber-100"
     style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 0 12px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 12px 14px);">
  <div class="container-wide flex items-center gap-3 py-2 text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold">
    <span class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">🤡</span>
    <p class="flex-1 text-pretty">
      <span class="uppercase tracking-[0.16em]">Satire</span> ·
      Everything below is a joke. None of it is real, accurate, or meant to be taken seriously.
      Don't cite it. Don't believe it. Don't screenshot out of context.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
